{
  "id": "fdai-system-overview",
  "version": 1,
  "updated": "2026-07-20",
  "locales": {
    "en": {
      "title": "FDAI system architecture",
      "description": "Signals enter a governed control plane and leave through approval-aware delivery paths.",
      "alt": "Azure changes, telemetry, operator requests, and scheduled probes enter Event Hubs. The FDAI control plane ingests each event, selects a trust tier, verifies the decision, applies the risk gate, and either executes, requests approval, or holds. Outcomes are delivered through remediation pull requests and recorded in PostgreSQL for the read-only console."
    },
    "ko": {
      "title": "FDAI system architecture",
      "description": "Signal은 governed control plane에 들어오고 approval-aware delivery path를 통해 나갑니다.",
      "alt": "Azure change, telemetry, operator request, scheduled probe가 Event Hubs로 들어갑니다. FDAI control plane은 각 event를 ingest하고 trust tier를 선택하며 decision을 verify하고 risk gate를 적용합니다. 그 결과는 execute, approval request 또는 hold로 이어집니다. Outcome은 remediation pull request로 전달되고 read-only console을 위해 PostgreSQL에 기록됩니다."
    }
  },
